Very knowledgeable about the content but his accent makes it pretty difficult to understand him, mainly because he also has a habit of speaking really quickly. Even the syllabus seemed disorganized. Really fair in terms of content on exams and assignments though and he makes it relatively easy to get a good grade.

Hes pretty funny if you get his jokes. He loves his Seinfeld. Alot of students have a hard time understanding him but he's not bad at all compared to some other ones here. Be prepared for his questions though. This guy will find any way to ask something and you have to answer it given the knowledge you have. He does let you say I dont know though.
